        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Billing",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " schema. It allows filtering based on several optional parameters such as provider ID, group ID, summary account number, and billing type. The procedure also logs the operation details, including any exceptions, using another stored procedure "
